# Vite (project root) — copy to .env
# Local dev:
VITE_API_URL=http://localhost:3001
#
# Production (read carefully):
# - This value is embedded when you run `vite build`. Set it in Netlify/Vercel/Railway
#   **Build** environment variables, not only on the server that runs Node.
# - If the API is on another domain, set the full API origin, e.g.:
#   VITE_API_URL=https://api.yourdomain.com
# - If the SPA and API share one domain and nginx proxies /api → Node, you can omit
#   VITE_API_URL at build time; the app will use the browser’s origin for API calls.
